715694f-a.title: Manhattan: 158th Street (West) - Amsterdam Avenue
715694f-a.text:
(1)  519-521 West 158th Street, north side, west of Amsterdaa
Avenue. Both are three-story frame houses.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 22
(2)
517 to 513 West 158th Street, north side, west of Amsterdam
Ave. Shown are 3 frame houses, No. 5l7 having a one story extension
at its front.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 23.
